ore complex. These territories contain **ancient mythological sites and Dreamfield anomalies**. Possible features include: - Fury Gateways - lost civilizations - Dreamfield rupture zones - unknown archetypal entities These regions are largely unexplored and represent major future story arcs. --- # F-Link Global Network F-Link is a neural integration system designed to connect human consciousness into a planetary communication network. Key components: - neural wafer implant - nanite integration - global data synchronization Major nodes appear in megacities around the world. When fully operational, the network forms a **planet-wide neural lattice**. ### System Status (Issue 1) GLOBAL F-LINK INTEGRATION 19% COMPLETE ESTIMATED TIME TO TOTALITY 400 CYCLES --- # Hidden Power Structures Beneath global politics operate several secret organizations. These groups manipulate both governments and religious institutions to shape the course of human civilization. Most citizens remain unaware of their existence. One of the most influential hidden powers is the **Order of the Black Sun**, which seeks to control the metaphysical infrastructure underlying the world. --- # The Planetary Transformation By the beginning of the story, three forces are converging simultaneously: 1. Technological Integration 2. Religious Prophecy 3. Mythological Awakening The interaction between these forces leads to the catastrophic event known as the **Quantum Fracture**. This event destabilizes the boundary between the Surface World and deeper layers of reality. --- # Narrative Importance The world map serves as the foundation for all global story arcs. Season One focuses primarily on: - Neo-Osaka - Saint Radian Institute - early F-Link deployment Future seasons gradually expand the scope to include global political conflicts and mythological territories. --- # Canonical Map Notes The world of Battle Eternal is intentionally designed to appear familiar while hiding deeper layers of truth. Human civilization occupies only part of the planet's true structure. Beyond the known regions lie territories where myth, consciousness, and reality intersect. These places will become increasingly important as the story unfolds.": {"path":null,"embeddings":{"TaylorAI/bge-micro-v2":{"vec":[-0.00941687,0.0002761,0.04591592,0.03692392,-0.00129117,0.01439614,-0.0022258,0.06764361,0.01594062,0.00166807,-0.0251969,-0.08316407,0.0496419,0.06567804,0.02101443,-0.03256131,-0.0813495,0.01410462,-0.02176607,0.01921345,0.14061259,-0.04848709,0.02363846,-0.05113957,-0.015802,0.01964012,-0.01869972,-0.03766896,-0.01747216,-0.23940927,-0.03734511,-0.00744552,-0.00398004,0.01190981,-0.05746673,0.00082856,-0.03891206,0.01016737,-0.09148739,0.03053541,0.00572581,0.06357072,0.02202072,-0.00949364,-0.02275973,-0.04739222,-0.04802398,0.03513504,-0.02204223,-0.0577356,0.04908621,-0.00533646,-0.00437035,0.02101972,0.03143503,0.04563709,0.0050949,0.01870164,0.04866791,-0.00252551,0.05298252,-0.01179105,-0.1840357,0.07717504,0.07229111,0.05249384,0.01738682,0.00632993,-0.04669825,-0.02677892,-0.07796222,0.0455145,-0.01576633,0.03847227,0.0386274,0.04586892,0.00259742,-0.05415881,-0.05582373,0.01579466,0.055423,0.10687387,-0.06503911,0.0050418,-0.04585922,0.02008285,0.01701184,-0.00607408,0.01383377,0.00965013,-0.05353655,0.02385326,0.03470117,0.03272297,0.00276022,-0.05630121,0.060388,-0.0071779,0.05905974,0.10457984,-0.01437269,0.00185322,0.04661668,0.02846925,0.10923194,-0.01829088,-0.03399551,-0.01830392,-0.05506005,0.01751079,0.00824649,-0.06337047,-0.06660256,-0.03547521,0.04107643,-0.03896291,0.05281113,0.04028935,-0.02212071,-0.05767438,-0.00881708,0.01737908,0.05561614,0.0237154,0.02958989,-0.01276382,0.03950203,0.01900536,0.0836169,-0.10695035,0.02462392,-0.01389088,-0.05231436,0.00960522,0.00416158,0.00672605,-0.01435291,0.01128321,-0.02072798,0.04030152,-0.01948468,-0.0075111,-0.00487916,-0.09525144,-0.0373125,0.07091797,-0.01563576,-0.01068388,-0.03115849,0.07291032,0.00486954,0.02878138,-0