6478451,0.03426759,0.06601464,0.02068031,0.01051705,-0.00530051,-0.03608925,-0.01451562,0.05801461,0.00911679,0.03977123,0.01940407,0.01924436,0.01734058,0.16147406,0.02422245,0.09125753,0.03548204,-0.0187414,-0.00010142,-0.03229968,0.02402611,-0.00043252,0.0119775,0.06436107,-0.0760143,-0.02528527,0.04558779,0.04312217,0.0068405,0.03552794,0.00592449,0.00474546,-0.0024533,0.03817661,0.07205251,0.0701545,-0.01042182,-0.04467978,-0.01198855,0.00466792,-0.00266599,-0.04495012,-0.06358189,0.01484155,-0.0628856,-0.0021578,0.02211272,0.00963167,-0.06572902,-0.02838297,-0.08235753,0.03189925,-0.04100381,-0.01815674,-0.02116505,-0.00019955],"last_embed":{"hash":"12mzurk","tokens":470}}},"text":null,"length":0,"last_read":{"hash":"12mzurk","at":1773342488728},"key":"Surface World.md###Battle Eternal World Atlas The **Surface World** of Battle Eternal in the year **2038** appears familiar to modern civilization, but beneath the illusion of normality lies a planetary system shaped by technological integration, religious upheaval, and hidden mythological forces. The world is divided into several major geopolitical regions, while deeper layers of reality operate through metaphysical structures unseen by most of humanity. This document defines the **canonical geography and global power structure** of the Battle Eternal universe. --- # Global Map Overview The world is divided into **five major civilization blocs** and several **restricted mythological territories**. ## Civilization Regions 1. Pacific Nexus 2. Western Hegemony 3. Eurasian Dominion 4. Southern Coalition 5. Sacred Belt ## Hidden Regions 1. Forbidden Expanse 2. Dreamfield Convergence Zones 3. Fury Gateways 4. Mythic Territories --- # Pacific Nexus ## Primary City **Neo-Osaka** Neo-Osaka is the most technologically advanced city in the world and serves as the global center of neural integration technology. Key elements: - headquarters of **F-Link neural infrastructure** - location of **Saint Radian Institute** - experimental Dreamfield research - high concentration of advanced AI systems The city functions as a **global technological nexus**, making it the most important strategic location on the planet. ### Cultural Identity Neo-Osaka blends ancient spiritual symbolism with ultra-modern cybernetic infrastructure. Shrines and temples coexist with towering data centers and corporate megastructures. --- # Western Hegemony The Western Hegemony represents the most economically powerful political alliance in the world. Characteristics: - multinational corporate dominance - financial control of global markets - strong media influence - advanced research universities Major megacities: - New Avalon - Neo-London - Pacifica Hidden influence from global elite councils shapes many of the Hegemony's decisions. --- # Eurasian Dominion The Eurasian Dominion is a centralized authoritarian superpower. Characteristics: - strict digital surveillance - strong military control - state-managed neural integration - limited civil freedoms The Dominion views F-Link primarily as a **tool of governance and societal control**. --- # Southern Coalition The Southern Coalition is a diverse alliance of rapidly developing nations. Characteristics: - emerging technological hubs - major population centers - strong cultural and religious diversity The region becomes a central battleground for ideological conflict once global prophecy movements emerge. --- # Sacred Belt The Sacred Belt is the world's largest concentration of historic religious centers. Cities include: - Neo-Venice - São Paulo - New Constantinople - Alexandria Prime During the early stages of F-Link deployment, many religious institutions reinterpret neural integration as a **new form of divine communion**. ## Communion Ritual Traditional Eucharist rituals evolve into **Neural Communion**. Instead of bread and wine, worshippers receive a **micro-neural wafer implant**. The ritual phrase: > \"Unify with God.\" This transformation ignites major theological and political conflicts worldwide. --- # Forbidden Expanse Large regions of the planet remain officially restricted. Public explanations include: - environmental collapse - extreme radiation - military quarantine zones The true reason is far more complex. These territories contain **ancient mythological sites and Dreamfield anomalies**. Possible features include: - Fury Gateways - lost civilizations - Dreamfield rupture zones - unknown archetypal entities These regions are largely unexplored and represent major future story arcs. --- # F-Link Global Network F-Link is a neural integration system designed to connect human consciousness into a planetary communication network. Key components: - neural wafer implant - nanite integration - global data synchronization Major nodes appear in megacities around the world. When fully operational, the network forms a **planet-wide neural lattice**. ### System Status (Issue 1) GLOBAL F-LINK INTEGRATION 19% COMPLETE ESTIMATED TIME TO TOTALITY 400 CYCLES --- # Hidden Power Structures Beneath global politics operate several secret organizations. These groups manipulate both governments and religious institutions to shape the course of human civilization. Most citizens remain unaware of their existence. One of the most influential hidden powers is the **Order of the Black Sun**, which seeks to control the metaphysical infrastructure underlying the world. --- # The Planetary Transformation By the beginning of the story, three forces are converging simultaneously: 1. Technological Integration 2. Religious Prophecy 3. Mythological Awakening The interaction between these forces leads to the catastrophic event known as the **Quantum Fracture**. This event destabilizes the boundary between the Surface World and deeper layers of reality. --- # Narrative Importance The world map serves as the foundation for all global story arcs. Season One focuses primarily on: - Neo-Osaka - Saint Radian Institute - early F-Link deployment Future seasons gradually expand the scope to include global political conflicts and mythological territories. --- # Canonical Map Notes The world of Battle Eternal is intentionally designed to appear familiar while hiding deeper layers of truth. Human civilization occupies only part of the planet's true structure. Beyond the known regions lie territories where myth, consciousness, and reality intersect. These places will become increasingly important as the story unfolds.","lines":[2,2],"size":5679,"outlinks":[],"class_name":"SmartBlock","last_embed":{"hash":"12mzurk","at":1773342488728}},

